                <string>Strength (GFF: Str). BYTE. Base strength; engine reads via ReadFieldBYTE in
                 ReadStatsFromGff. Default when missing: 0. In-game: affects melee damage, carry
                 weight, Str-based skills. Modders: valid range 0–255; typical values 8–20. Modifier
                 = (Str - 10) / 2 (min -5).</string>
               </property>
               <property name="sizePolicy">
                <sizepolicy hsizetype="Preferred" vsizetype="Preferred">
